# Intuition
We need to fill the bags full as many as possible so we need to target the bags having less space so we use sorting.

# Approach
We need to make an array with remaining space and sort the array. Now let us traverse the array and fill those. If it is filled update the answer.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(NogN)

- Space complexity:
O(N)

# Code
