missingRocks[i] is the number of rocks needed to fill the i-th bag.

2. By sorting missingRocks, we find which of the bags requires the least amount of rocks to add, those by filling from the begining of the sorted missingRocks vector we will $$maximize$$ the amount of bags filled. 
